OL,3,CParents of toddler killed by pensioner
OL,4,Cwith dementia call for DVLA changes
OL,6,FSTV reporter Laura Alderman speaks to
OL,7,Fthe parents of Xander Irvine, the
OL,8,Fthree-year-old who died in a collision
OL,9,Fwith a car driven by a woman with
OL,10,Fdementia
OL,12,FThe parents of a toddler killed after
OL,13,Fbeing knocked down by a car driven by
OL,14,Fa woman with dementia have spoken for
OL,15,Fthe first time and are calling for the
OL,16,FDVLA to change the system for older
OL,17,Fdrivers.
