OL,3,CParents of toddler killed by pensioner
OL,4,Cwith dementia call for DVLA changes
OL,6,FThree-year-old Xander Irvine was
OL,7,Fwalking with his mum, Victoria, on
OL,8,FMorningside Road in Edinburgh on June
OL,9,F30, 2020 when they were hit by a car
OL,10,Fdriven by a 91-year-old woman with
OL,11,Fundiagnosed dementia.
OL,13,FXander died in the city's Royal
OL,14,FHospital for Sick Children several
OL,15,Fhours later.
OL,17,FA fatal accident inquiry into his
OL,18,Fdeath found the collision was caused
OL,19,Fby Edith Duncan losing control of the
OL,20,Fvehicle entirely due to her inability
OL,21,Fto perform a routine turning manoeuvre.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
