OL,6,FMs Duncan, who was facing prosecution
OL,7,Ffor the incident, died a year later.
OL,9,FThe inquiry, which concluded in
OL,10,FOctober 2024, found the collision
OL,11,Fcould have been avoided if Ms Duncan's
OL,12,Fcognitive ability had been properly
OL,13,Fassessed and if authorities had
OL,14,Fsubsequently moved to revoke her
OL,15,Fdriving licence.
OL,17,FSpeaking exclusively to STV News for
OL,18,Fthe first time about their son's
OL,19,Fdeath, Victoria and her husband Paul
OL,20,Fare calling for positive change to
OL,21,Fhappen in Xander's name.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
