OL,6,FPaul said: "Sitting through the fatal
OL,7,Faccident inquiry I heard a lot of
OL,8,Fexperts say there's a big rise in
OL,9,Fcognitive decline and that it's only
OL,10,Fgoing to get worse.
OL,12,F"It's only inevitable that something
OL,13,Flike this might happen again, more
OL,14,Fthan likely will, so this is why we
OL,15,Fwant to try and push the government
OL,16,Fand the DVLA to make these
OL,17,Frecommendations that the sheriff has
OL,18,Fcome up with."
