OL,6,FPaul added: "The house was always full
OL,7,Fof joy, laughter, singing, we were
OL,8,Falways just having a carry-on and then
OL,9,Fjust that one day it was all just
OL,10,Fripped away from us...and then the
OL,11,Fstart of this life.
OL,13,F"For me, I just remember the silence.
OL,14,FI sat at the window just staring out
OL,15,Finto space, for what must have been
OL,16,Fclose to a couple of months.
