OL,6,F"It just completely turns your life
OL,7,Fupside down. I don't think we'll ever
OL,8,Fcome to terms with it, especially
OL,9,Fgiven the circumstances and knowing
OL,10,Fthat had there been something in place
OL,11,F` something a bit more robust than the
OL,12,Fcurrent system ` then we might still
OL,13,Fhave our boy."
OL,15,FCurrent DVLA rules mean once a driver
OL,16,Freaches 70, they need to renew their
OL,17,Flicence every three years.
