OL,3,CParents of toddler killed by pensioner
OL,4,Cwith dementia call for DVLA changes
OL,6,FThis is done through a self-
OL,7,Fcertification of fitness to drive,
OL,8,Fdeclaring any disabilities of
OL,9,Fconditions such as dementia or sight
OL,10,Floss.
OL,12,FThe inquiry's sheriff described the
OL,13,Fcurrent system as "significantly
OL,14,Fdefective" and recommended an overhaul
OL,15,Fof the system including limiting self-
OL,16,Fcertification to people aged under 80
OL,17,Fand requiring anyone over 80 to
OL,18,Fundertake a cognitive assessment
OL,19,Fbefore a renewed licence is granted.
OL,26,@uD@SOUvD@JO]
