OL,6,FVictoria said: "We felt a certain
OL,7,Famount of relief that all the experts
OL,8,Fwere in agreement that we needed to
OL,9,Fbring in these proportionate changes
OL,10,Fnow and we need to modernise the way
OL,11,Fwe assess older drivers.
OL,13,F"We certainly feel this is something
OL,14,Fwe want to see sooner rather than
OL,15,Flater. We're appealing to the
OL,16,Fgovernment and the DVLA to step up and
OL,17,Fmake this a priority.
