OL,6,FVictoria said she has a "real fear"
OL,7,Fabout something similar happening
OL,8,Fagain, adding: "We don't want to see
OL,9,Fanyone else go through anything like
OL,10,Fwhat we've been through."
OL,12,FVictoria and Paul said sticking
OL,13,Ftogether and remembering special times
OL,14,Fwith their son is what gets them
OL,15,Fthrough the tough times.
